==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Taborite
<hw>Ta"bor*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld>
<def>One of certain Bohemian reformers who suffered persecution in the
fifteenth century; -- so called from <xex>Tabor</xex>, a hill or
fortress where they encamped during a part of their struggles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tabour</ent>⟦br⟧
